### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  FinFlow API — pruebas rápidas
###  Usa la extensión "REST Client" de VS Code (Send Request) o copia
###  los curl equivalentes del final del archivo.
###  Flujo: ejecuta LOGIN, copia el token y pégalo en @token.
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@base = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = PEGA_AQUI_EL_TOKEN

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Categorías
GET {{base}}/categorias

### Registro
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nombre": "Juan Pérez", "email": "juan@test.mx", "password": "secreto1" }

### Login (usuario demo — corre `npm run seed` antes)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "demo@finflow.mx", "password": "demo1234" }

### Login con Google
POST {{base}}/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "google@test.mx", "nombre": "Usuario Google" }

### Usuario actual
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Dashboard
GET {{base}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Historial completo
GET {{base}}/transacciones
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Historial — solo ingresos
GET {{base}}/transacciones?tipo=ingreso
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Historial — solo gastos (5 más recientes)
GET {{base}}/transacciones?tipo=gasto&limite=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear gasto
POST {{base}}/transacciones
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "tipo": "gasto", "monto": 84.50, "descripcion": "Supermercado",
  "categoria": "Comida", "metodo_pago": "Tarjeta", "comercio": "Súper Central" }

### Crear ingreso recurrente
POST {{base}}/transacciones
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "tipo": "ingreso", "monto": 2850, "descripcion": "Nómina mensual",
  "recurrente": true, "frecuencia": "mensual" }

### Actualizar transacción (reemplaza :id)
PUT {{base}}/transacciones/REEMPLAZA_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "monto": 99.90 }

### Borrar transacción (reemplaza :id)
DELETE {{base}}/transacciones/REEMPLAZA_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Perfil
GET {{base}}/perfil
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Editar perfil + ajustes
PUT {{base}}/perfil
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "nombre": "Alex R", "ajustes": { "notificaciones": true, "biometria": true } }

### Config de ingreso
PUT {{base}}/config/ingreso
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "monto": 1500, "frecuencia": "quincenal" }

### Ahorros
PUT {{base}}/ahorros
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "meta": 12000, "actual": 5000 }

### Coach IA
POST {{base}}/coach
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Leer ticket (imageBase64 de ejemplo: 1px PNG)
POST {{base}}/leer-ticket
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "imageBase64": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAQAAAC1HAwCAAAAC0lEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==", "mediaType": "image/png" }

### ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### Equivalentes en curl (terminal):
###
### curl http://localhost:3000/api/health
###
### TOKEN=$(curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login \
###   -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
###   -d '{"email":"demo@finflow.mx","password":"demo1234"}' \
###   | python3 -c 'import sys,json;print(json.load(sys.stdin)["data"]["token"])')
###
### curl http://localhost:3000/api/dashboard -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN"
###
### curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/transacciones \
###   -H "Authorization: Bearer $TOKEN" -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
###   -d '{"tipo":"gasto","monto":84.5,"descripcion":"Súper","categoria":"Comida","metodo_pago":"Tarjeta"}'
